description:
Rocky is quite a character. This 20-year-old straight boy is full of energy and has something to say about almost everything.

I actually wish all of my models could be as fun as Rocky. He was cracking jokes from the first minute I met him, and from there it was nonstop — pulling his pants off in the car, back flips in the park, and a lot of "cheesy" posing that only he could pull off!

He's definitely an open book... he has a girlfriend who knew all about his trip out to meet us (is it just me, or are the girlfriends getting more liberal?).

Rocky also has a really nice body, with a great set of abs and a beautiful ass!
title: Rocky
